data.description: PRICE IMPROVMENT!! Welcome to this captivating three-bedroom, two-bath home with a characterful painted brick exterior. The beautifully landscaped backyard is a picturesque retreat, and the huge back porch provides a perfect outdoor sanctuary.  A unique feature of this property is the detached man cave, a separate building that offers a private and versatile space for your hobbies, work, or leisure activities. Whether you envision it as a home office, art studio, or just as a storage building, this detached building allows for endless possibilities.  Step inside the main house, and you'll be welcomed by a fresh and inviting interior, adorned with tasteful finishes. The home boasts a desirable split plan, with large bedrooms, this layout provides enhanced privacy and convenience, making it an ideal choice for families or those who enjoy hosting guests.  The kitchen boasts elegant granite countertops, providing a luxurious touch to your culinary experiences. The large eat-in kitchen is perfect for family gatherings and casual meals, making it a central hub for everyday living.  The home has been lovingly maintained, with a newer roof ensuring durability and peace of mind. With its thoughtful layout, well-crafted design, and unique detached man cave, this house offers both comfort and functionality.  Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a home with such distinctive features. Schedule a viewing today and experience the allure of this property's delightful interior, enchanting backyard, and the practicality of its split plan. Welcome to your new home, where every day promises to be extraordinary.  Butcher block island NOT included. All measurements to be verified by the buyer.
